translation[13]{c,v,t}:
  42,32,Uski nishaniyon mein se hain yeh jahaz (ships) jo samandar mein pahadon ki tarah nazar aate hain
  42,33,Allah jab chahey hawa ko saakin (motionless) karde aur yeh samandar ki peeth (back) par khade reh jayein. Ismein badi nishaniyan hain har us shaks ke liye jo kamal darja sabr o shukar karne wala ho
  42,34,Ya (unpar sawar honay walon ke) bahut se gunahon se dar guzar karte huey unke chandh hi kartooton ki padash mein unhein dubo (drown) de
  42,35,Aur us waqt hamari aayat mein jhagade karne walon ko pata chal jaaye ke unke liye koi jaaye panaah nahin hai
  42,36,"Jo kuch bhi tum logon ko diya gaya hai woh mehaz duniya ki chand roza zindagi ka sar o saaman hai, aur jo kuch Allah ke haan hai woh behtar bhi hai aur payedar bhi. Woh un logon ke liye hai jo imaan laye hain aur apne Rubb par bharosa karte hain"
  42,37,Jo badey badey gunahon aur be hayayi ke kaamon se parheiz karte hain aur agar gussa aa jaye to darguzar kar jatey hain
  42,38,"Jo apne Rubb ka hukum maante hain, namaz qayam karte hain, apne maamlaat aapas ke mashware se chalate hain, humne jo kuch bhi rizq unhein diya hai us mein se kharch karte hain"
  42,39,Aur jab unpar zyadati ki jaati hai to uska muqaabla karte hain
  42,40,"Burayi ka badla waisi hi burayi hai, phir jo koi maaf karde aur islaah karey uska ajar Allah ke zimme hai. Allah zaalimon ko pasand nahin karta"
  42,41,Aur jo log zulm honay ke baad badla lein unko malamat nahin ki ja sakti
  42,42,Malamat ke mustahiq to woh hain jo dusron par zulm karte hain aur zameen mein na haqq zyadatiyan karte hain. Aisey logon ke liye dardnaak azaab hai
  42,43,"Albatta jo shaks sabr se kaam le aur darguzar karey, to yeh badi ulul azmi ke kaamon mein se hai"
  42,44,Jis ko Allah hi gumraahi mein phenk de us ka koi sambhaalne wala Allah ke baad nahin hai. Tum dekho ge yeh zaalim jab azaab dekhenge to kahenge ab palatne ki bhi koi sabeel hai